data.description: This fabulous patio home harmoniously blends both indoor and outdoor living. The open-concept living, dining and kitchen all provide access to the functional and beautiful outdoor living areas, designed to provide mosquito-free, cool summer evenings, warm winter spaces, and easy access to the neighborhood pool which is located just a few steps from the private patio. Abundant natural light creates a bright and cheery living space and primary suite. The spacious primary bathroom features a dual vanity with knee-space, natural light, large closet, and walk-in shower. Two guest bedrooms share a generously sized guest bathroom. This unique property is located on a quiet street in highly desirable Woodcreek, popular with people who love to walk and jog, and for all of the amenities including the community pool, parks, and walking trails. Conveniently located, this home is just minutes from Scott & White Hospital, many restaurants, grocery stores, and retail.
